<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
    @font-face { font-family: 'Sarabun'; src: url('https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/sarabun/v13/DtVjJx26TKEr37c9aBVJmg.ttf') format('truetype'); }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Sarabun', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.3; color: #000; }
    .page { width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm; padding: 2mm; background: #fff; }
    .header-container { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5mm; margin-bottom: 3mm; }
    .header-logo img { height: 56px; width: auto; }
    .company-header { flex: 1; }
    .company-header-thai { background-color: #1a3a52; color: #fff; padding: 2mm 5mm; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1mm; }
    .company-header-thai p { font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; }
    .company-header-english { background-color: #8f4e3b; color: #fff; padding: 2mm 5mm; text-align: center; margin-top: -4px; }
    .company-header-english h1 { font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; }
    .company-info { font-size: 8.8pt; line-height: 1.25; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3mm; }
    .doc-details { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 3mm; font-size: 10pt; }
    .doc-details td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 1mm 1.2mm; vertical-align: top; font-weight: 400; }
    .work-type-box { text-align: center; vertical-align: middle !important; }
    .work-type-box .th { font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; }
    .work-type-box .en { font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; }
    .tax-row { width: 100%; text-align: center; font-size: 10pt; margin-bottom: 2.5mm; }
    .tax-check { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin: 0 10px; }
    .box { width: 11px; height: 11px; border: 1px solid #000; display: inline-block; position: relative; top: 1px; }
    .box.checked::after { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 2px; top: 0px; width: 5px; height: 8px; border: solid #000; border-width: 0 1.5px 1.5px 0; transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .main-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; margin-bottom: 5mm; font-size: 10pt; }
    .main-table th, .main-table td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 1.5mm 1.8mm; vertical-align: top; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-wrap: break-word; }
    .main-table th { text-align: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 9.2pt; line-height: 1.2; background: #f8f8f8; }
    .col-item { width: 8%; text-align: center; }
    .col-desc { width: 47%; }
    .col-qty { width: 15%; text-align: right; }
    .col-price { width: 15%; text-align: right; }
    .col-amount { width: 15%; text-align: right; }
    .empty-row td { height: 7mm; }
    .summary-blank { background: #fff; }
    .summary-thai { font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle !important; font-style: italic; padding: 2.8mm; line-height: 1.45; }
    .summary-label { text-align: left; font-size: 10pt; vertical-align: middle !important; }
    .summary-percent { text-align: center; font-size: 10pt; vertical-align: middle !important; }
    .summary-value { text-align: right; font-size: 10pt; vertical-align: middle !important; }
    .summary-grand .summary-label, .summary-grand .summary-value { font-weight: bold; }
    .signatures { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2mm; margin-top: 7mm; margin-bottom: 4mm; }
    .sig-box { flex: 1; text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; }
    .sig-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; height: 14mm; margin-bottom: 2mm; width: 84%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; position: relative; }
    .sig-line img { max-height: 13mm; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
    .sig-label { font-weight: normal; margin-top: 1mm; }
    .payment-terms { font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; margin: 2mm 0 2mm; }
    .conditions { font-size: 9pt; line-height: 1.35; margin-top: 1.5mm; margin-bottom: 2mm; }
    .footer { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; font-size: 8.8pt; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin-top: 2mm; padding-top: 2mm; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <% 
    const docNo = ((typeof pattycashNumber !== 'undefined' && pattycashNumber) ? pattycashNumber : '-');
    const itemList = (typeof items !== 'undefined' && Array.isArray(items)) ? items : [];
    const fmt2 = (v) => {
      const n = Number(v);
      return Number.isFinite(n) ? n.toLocaleString('en-US', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) : '0.00';
    };
    const qtyFmt = (v) => {
      const n = Number(v);
      return Number.isFinite(n) ? n.toFixed(2) : '0.00';
    };
    const taxPct = Number((typeof vatPercent !== 'undefined' ? vatPercent : 0) || 0);
    const withholdPct = Number((typeof withholdingPercent !== 'undefined' ? withholdingPercent : 0) || 0);
    const paymentText =
      ((typeof paymentTerms !== 'undefined' && paymentTerms) ? String(paymentTerms) : '') ||
      ((typeof remark !== 'undefined' && remark) ? String(remark) : '') ||
      'เครดิต 30 Days';
    const _purchaseBy =
      ((typeof purchaseBy !== 'undefined' && purchaseBy) ? purchaseBy : '') ||
      ((typeof requester !== 'undefined' && requester) ? requester : '-') || '-';
  %>

  <div class="page">
    <div class="header-container">
      <div class="header-logo">
        <% if (typeof logo !== 'undefined' && logo) { %><img src="<%= logo %>" alt="Company Logo" /><% } else { %><h2>EXPERTEAM</h2><% } %>
      </div>
      <div class="company-header">
        <div class="company-header-thai"><p>บริษัท เอ็กเพิททีม จำกัด</p></div>
        <div class="company-header-english"><h1><%= (typeof companyName !== 'undefined' && companyName) ? companyName : 'EXPERTEAM COMPANY LIMITED' %></h1></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="company-info">
      <p><%= (typeof companyAddress !== 'undefined' && companyAddress) ? companyAddress : '-' %></p>
      <p>โทรศัพท์: <%= (typeof phone !== 'undefined' && phone) ? phone : '-' %>, โทรสาร: <%= (typeof fax !== 'undefined' && fax) ? fax : '-' %> Email: <%= (typeof email !== 'undefined' && email) ? email : '-' %>, Website: <%= (typeof website !== 'undefined' && website) ? website : '-' %></p>
    </div>

    <table class="doc-details">
      <tr>
        <td style="width: 30%;"><strong>งาน Job:</strong><br><%= (typeof jobName !== 'undefined' && jobName) ? jobName : '-' %></td>
        <td rowspan="3" class="work-type-box" style="width: 20%;"><div class="th">ใบเงินสด</div><div class="en">PATTY CASH</div></td>
        <td style="width: 20%;"><strong>เลขที่เอกสาร</strong><br><%= docNo %></td>
        <td style="width: 30%;"><strong>วันที่</strong><br>Date :<br><%= (typeof date !== 'undefined' && date) ? date : '-' %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2"><strong>สถานที่ ( Location )</strong><br><%= (typeof deliveryLocation !== 'undefined' && deliveryLocation) ? deliveryLocation : '-' %></td>
        <td><strong>Project code :</strong><br><%= (typeof projectCode !== 'undefined' && projectCode) ? projectCode : '-' %></td>
        <td><strong>C.C. No.</strong><br><%= (typeof ccNo !== 'undefined' && ccNo) ? ccNo : '-' %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2"><strong>Trader :</strong><br><%= (typeof trader !== 'undefined' && trader) ? trader : ((typeof supplier !== 'undefined' && supplier) ? supplier : '-') %></td>
        <td><strong>Job No.</strong><br><%= (typeof jobNo !== 'undefined' && jobNo) ? jobNo : '-' %></td>
        <td><strong>Purchase by :</strong><br><%= _purchaseBy %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="tax-row">
      <span>อัตราภาษี</span>
      <span class="tax-check"><span class="box <%= taxPct === 7 ? 'checked' : '' %>"></span><span>ร้อยละ 7</span></span>
      <span class="tax-check"><span class="box <%= taxPct === 0 ? 'checked' : '' %>"></span><span>ร้อยละ 0</span></span>
    </div>

    <table class="main-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="col-item">ลำดับ<br>ITEM</th>
          <th class="col-desc">รายการสินค้า<br>DESCRIPTION</th>
          <th class="col-qty">จำนวน : หน่วย<br>QUANTITY UNIT</th>
          <th class="col-price">หน่วยละ<br>UNIT PRICE</th>
          <th class="col-amount">ราคารวม<br>AMOUNT</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% itemList.forEach((item, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td class="col-item"><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td class="col-desc"><%= item.description || item.name || '' %></td>
            <td class="col-qty"><%= qtyFmt(item.quantity) %> <%= item.unit || '' %></td>
            <td class="col-price"><%= fmt2(item.unitPrice) %></td>
            <td class="col-amount"><%= fmt2(item.amount || (Number(item.quantity || 0) * Number(item.unitPrice || 0))) %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }); %>
        <% for (let i = itemList.length; i < 10; i++) { %>
          <tr class="empty-row"><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
        <% } %>

        <tr>
          <td class="summary-blank"></td>
          <td class="summary-thai" rowspan="6">(<%= (typeof grandTotalText !== 'undefined' && grandTotalText) ? grandTotalText : 'ศูนย์บาทถ้วน' %>)</td>
          <td class="summary-label" colspan="2">รวมราคา</td>
          <td class="summary-value"><%= fmt2((typeof subTotal !== 'undefined') ? subTotal : 0) %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td class="summary-blank"></td><td class="summary-label" colspan="2">หัก ส่วนลด</td><td class="summary-value">0.00</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="summary-blank"></td><td class="summary-label">หัก ภาษี ณ ที่จ่าย</td><td class="summary-percent"><%= withholdPct %>%</td><td class="summary-value"><%= fmt2((typeof withholding !== 'undefined') ? withholding : 0) %></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="summary-blank"></td><td class="summary-label" colspan="2">รวมราคาหลังหัก</td><td class="summary-value"><%= fmt2((typeof subAfterWithholding !== 'undefined') ? subAfterWithholding : 0) %></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="summary-blank"></td><td class="summary-label" colspan="2">จำนวนภาษีมูลค่าเพิ่ม <%= taxPct %>%</td><td class="summary-value"><%= fmt2((typeof vat !== 'undefined') ? vat : 0) %></td></tr>
        <tr class="summary-grand"><td class="summary-blank"></td><td class="summary-label" colspan="2">จำนวนเงินทั้งสิ้น</td><td class="summary-value"><%= fmt2((typeof grandTotal !== 'undefined') ? grandTotal : 0) %></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="signatures">
      <div class="sig-box"><div class="sig-line"><% if (typeof sig1 !== 'undefined' && sig1) { %><img src="<%= sig1 %>" alt="signature"><% } %></div><div class="sig-label">ผู้สั่งซื้อ</div></div>
      <div class="sig-box"><div class="sig-line"><% if (typeof sig2 !== 'undefined' && sig2) { %><img src="<%= sig2 %>" alt="signature"><% } %></div><div class="sig-label">Project / Originator</div></div>
      <div class="sig-box"><div class="sig-line"><% if (typeof sig3 !== 'undefined' && sig3) { %><img src="<%= sig3 %>" alt="signature"><% } %></div><div class="sig-label">Store</div></div>
      <div class="sig-box"><div class="sig-line"></div><div class="sig-label">ผู้อนุมัติ</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="payment-terms"><strong>เงื่อนไขการชำระเงิน:</strong> <%= paymentText %></div>

    <div class="conditions">
      <div>เงื่อนไข 1) โปรดระบุเลขที่ใบสั่งซื้อ ในใบเสร็จรับเงิน / ใบกำกับภาษี หรือ ใบเสนอราคา ทุกครั้งเพื่อสะดวกในการอ้างอิงและชำระเงิน</div>
      <div>2) เมื่อรับใบสั่งซื้อถือว่ายอมรับเงื่อนไขข้างต้น และเงื่อนไขที่แนบมาด้วย</div>
      <div>3) โปรดแนบใบสั่งซื้อ สำเนา เมื่อมาวางบิลเรียกเก็บเงิน</div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div><p>Page <%= (typeof page !== 'undefined' && page) ? page : '1/1' %></p></div>
      <div><p><%= (typeof formCode !== 'undefined' && formCode) ? formCode : '-' %></p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
